,0);">=E2=9C=B2&nbsp;<span style=3D"color: rgb(0,0,0);">All settings but <e=
m>servers</em> are only available with memcache<u>d</u>&nbsp;php extension,=
 for more information on these settings and which version of php-memcache<u=
>d</u> they are available in, see:&nbsp;<a href=3D"http://php.net/Memcached=
" class=3D"external-link" rel=3D"nofollow">http://php.net/Memcached</a></sp=
an></span><br>=E2=9C=B8</span>&nbsp;If you are on eZ Publish 5.1, make sure=
 to update Stash and StashBundle to get access to these settings.</p>
